<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .pin-code { font-size: 48px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; color: #667eea; margin: 30px 0; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; text-align: center; color: #666; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>UniMeet</h1>
            <p>Password Reset PIN Code</p>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Hello {{ user.name }},</h2>
        
        <p>You requested to reset your password for your UniMeet account. Use the following PIN code to verify your identity:</p>
        
        <div class="pin-code">{{ pinCode }}</div>
        
        <p>This PIN code will expire in 15 minutes for security reasons.</p>
        
        <p>If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email. Your account remains secure.</p>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 UniMeet. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>